history_model

Class HistoryStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • history_model.HistoryStore

  • public class HistoryStore
extends java.lang.Object
    This class serves as the storage class for all of the user's Hiking History. It takes each history object created through the user going on a hike and collects it into a linked list. The class has very general methods of find, remove, size, etc.
    Author:
    Nick Broome
